<div class="bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">About Our Store</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg leading-6 text-gray-500">
        Welcome to our online marketplace, where quality meets convenience.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="h-64 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <%= image_tag "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472851294608-062f824d29cc", 
                class: "h-full w-full object-cover",
                alt: "Modern storefront" %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:pl-8">
          <div class="text-base max-w-prose mx-auto lg:max-w-none">
            <p class="text-base text-indigo-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">Our Story</p>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-3xl leading-8 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Growing Together</h3>
            <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-gray-500">
              Founded with a passion for bringing quality products to our customers, we've grown from a small local shop
              to a trusted online marketplace. Our journey began with a simple idea: make shopping easier and more enjoyable
              for everyone.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-32">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <p class="text-base text-indigo-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">What We Stand For</p>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Our Values</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="pt-6">
            <div class="flow-root rounded-lg bg-gray-50 px-6 pb-8 shadow-lg">
              <div class="-mt-6">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-indigo-500 p-3 shadow-lg">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Quality First</h3>
                <p class="mt-5 text-base text-gray-500">
                  We carefully select each product to ensure it meets our high standards of quality and value.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-6">
            <div class="flow-root rounded-lg bg-gray-50 px-6 pb-8 shadow-lg">
              <div class="-mt-6">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-indigo-500 p-3 shadow-lg">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Customer Service</h3>
                <p class="mt-5 text-base text-gray-500">
                  Our dedicated support team is always ready to help you with any questions or concerns.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-6">
            <div class="flow-root rounded-lg bg-gray-50 px-6 pb-8 shadow-lg">
              <div class="-mt-6">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-indigo-500 p-3 shadow-lg">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Global Reach</h3>
                <p class="mt-5 text-base text-gray-500">
                  We deliver to customers worldwide, bringing quality products to your doorstep wherever you are.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-32">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-base text-indigo-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">Looking Forward</p>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500">
            To provide our customers with the best shopping experience possible, offering carefully curated products
            at competitive prices while maintaining the highest standards of customer service and satisfaction.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> 